
# DEPLOY COM CODEPIPELINE

git add .
git commit -m "sua mensagem"
git push origin main
# Pronto. O pipeline faz o resto.
Acompanhe em: https://sa-east-1.console.aws.amazon.com/codesuite/codepipeline/pipelines/prontivus-pipeline/view

Deploy manual (fallback, se o pipeline estiver com problema):


# No EC2:
pm2 stop prontivus
cd /opt/prontivus
git pull origin main
npm ci --legacy-peer-deps
npx prisma generate
cat > lib/generated/prisma/index.ts << 'EOF'
export * from './enums';
EOF
npx prisma migrate deploy
npm run build:production
pm2 start infrastructure/ecosystem.config.js


